<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="main_screen">
    <title>Main Screen</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>The main screen allows you to perform system scans, run virus database updates, and configure settings such as scheduled virus scans.</p>
        <fig>
            <image href="../images/main_screen.png" width="500" alt="ClamWin's Main Screen"></image>
        </fig>
        <p>You can open the main console from the start menu, or the Windows task bar.</p>
        <p>The following table describes the actions available in <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name"/>'s main screen</p>
        <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_ywy_3c4_nvb">
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <p>Action</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <p>Description</p>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry><p>Update virus database files</p></entry>
                        <entry><p>Click <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/mainui_update_bd"/> to manually update <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name"/>'s virus database files.</p>
                        <p>For more information see (link to topic)</p></entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry><p>Scan for virus and malware</p></entry>
                        <entry>
                            <note type="important">
                                <p conref="../conrefs_variables/notes_conref.xml#notes_conref/p_hcd_jlj_4vb"/>
                                <p conref="../conrefs_variables/notes_conref.xml#notes_conref/p_vkg_jlj_4vb"/>
                            </note>
                            <p>
                                <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name"/> allows you to perform scans of files, folders and programs executing in your computer. </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <p><b>Full system scan</b>: Select the drive where your operating system is installed and click <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/mainui_scan_files"/>.</p>
                                    <note type="tip">
                                        <p conref="../conrefs_variables/notes_conref.xml#notes_conref/p_k2x_4rj_4vb"/>
                                    </note>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p><b>Scan a file, folder, or external drive</b>: Select the file or folder you want to scan and click <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/mainui_scan_files"/>.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p><b>Scan computer memory</b>: Click <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/mainui_scan_ram"/>.</p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>For more information about scanning for viruses, see <xref href="scan_computer.xml"/>.</p>
                    </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry><p>Check for program updates</p></entry>
                        <entry><p>Go to <menucascade>
                                    <uicontrol>Help</uicontrol>
                                    <uicontrol>Check Latest Version</uicontrol>
                                </menucascade> to verify if you have the latest version of <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name"/></p></entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry><p>Open the settings screen</p></entry>
                        <entry>
                            <p>Configure all of <ph conkeyref="ClamWinVARS/short_product_name"/>'s settings, such as scanning options, email alerts or scheduled scans.</p>
                            <p>For more information, see [link to topic]</p>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </conbody>
</concept>
